/>\n根本冇得比"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"明明就係有班細路嘅父母以講廣東話為恥<br />\n佢地寧願細路講英文同普通話都唔想佢地講廣東話<br />\n而且係受到普教中嘅逼害先搞到佢地咁"},{"pid":"64922ad4e123b9a39e5b1c8a24618320008fa755","tid":752603,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T13:49:26.000Z","msg":"以色列人有猶太教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a5f1ab4fb2e363a115f946b9f06caf23b4faf2","tid":752603,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"128b82fc11e6664f4ba7ab5ee527ef7c3e73e9e5","tid":752603,"uid":190928,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"夠以色列人好抽咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人哋用六日收四個國家皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"如果中國分裂成多個國家<br />\n例如 廣州國, 深圳國, 之類<br />\n<br />\n相信香港都有能力打嬴四個國家........."}]}